        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "| Design Change | KPI Propagation |\n|---|---|\n| Vehicle Weight ↑ | payload ↓ → utilization ↓ → contribution ↓ |\n| Floor Height ↑ | conversion ↓ → trips ↓ |\n| Refill Time ↑ | uptime ↓ → fleet availability ↓ |\n| Berth Count ↓ | queue ↑ → dispatch delay ↑ |\n| H2 Supply ↓ | energy margin ↓ → HOLD / STOP |"
